column2: select distinct top # star.ra, star.dec, #* (star.ra  plate.racen) /cos (plate.deccen*PI () /#) as x, #* (star.dec  plate.deccen) as y, obj.j as mag from apogeestar as star join apogeeObject as obj on star.target_id = obj.target_id join apogeePlate as plate on star.location_id = plate.location_id where plate.plate = # order by mag
